  <chapter xml:id="ch1">
    <title>Getting Started</title>
    <para>Welcome to this guide. This chapter covers the basics.</para>
    <section>
      <title>Installation</title>
      <para>To install, run:</para>
      <programlisting>apt install my-package</programlisting>
      <warning>
        <para>Always backup your data before installation.</para>
      </warning>
    </section>
    <section>
      <title>Configuration</title>
      <para>Edit the configuration file <filename>/etc/my-package/config.xml</filename>.</para>
      <tip>
        <para>Use <option>--verbose</option> flag for detailed output.</para>
      </tip>
    </section>
  </chapter>

